What is Istio?

Istio - is a "service mesh".

service mesh, k8s is not enough. Extra layer of software you deploy alongside your cluster (eg K8s)

implements some "mesh logic", telemetry, tracing

istio adds side-car (proxy) into pods with app. iptables configuration.

istio-system namespace. -> single pod istiod (istio daemon) (used to be called "pilot").

proxies are collectively called the "Data plane" in istio.
istio-system - "control plane". Kiali UI.

